	<text_base_description>As one of the most iconic residential buildings in Pacific Heights, Broadway Towers is a renowned example of the mid-century aesthetic in the heart of the north side. With floor to ceiling windows across the entire home, this 1 bed / 1 bath home is bright and flooded with light. Relax or work from home on your private terrace that spans the entire width of the unit. The oversized living and dining room have a peekaboo view of the Golden Gate Bridge and direct walkout to the terrace. In the bedroom, walk out to your private terrace and take advantage of the large, walk-in closet. Updated, modern kitchen and bathroom. Freshly painted, with new carpet and blinds. Doorman building with professional building management and one-car parking. HOA includes professional management, water, cable, radiant heat, building insurance and earthquake insurance. All the best of Pacific Heights, Cow Hollow and the Marina are within walking distance.  </text_base_description>
